{"tid":420215,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"本將軍 已成功咒死賤種蝗卡華積 心臟病發","createTime":"2017-10-01T08:18:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-01T09:27:40.000Z","uid":54373,"like":4,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5c440df1674022ca234f92436f76a162da292b90","tid":420215,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T08:18:00.000Z","msg":"一同慶賀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7407eadd16cca9c6474a787a8a8b345a659065b6","tid":420215,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T08:19:48.000Z","msg":"真真開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f7b3f995b62a49eeac3056e2cdf3f59a8235eb3","tid":420215,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T08:21:00.000Z","msg":"弊！卡華積心臟病無限期休戰<br />\n7小時前<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=ZZTUqjObpp05G%2FEC0l3KCLr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=7d82843f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】皇家馬德里於周六宣佈，右閘丹尼爾卡華積因為心臟問題，暫時無限期休戰。<br />\n<br />\n丹尼爾卡華積（Dani Carvajal）今季踢足皇家馬德里所有比賽的每1分鐘，是右閘頭號人選，但現在因為其心臟問題，需要長時間治療才能痊癒，所以在健康為上的大前題下，將會全面休戰，有指他至少要養病1個半月。<br />\n<br />\n由於皇馬已有兩名左閘馬些路及迪奧靴南迪斯養傷，如今丹尼爾卡華積又要養病，因此在周日西甲主場迎戰愛斯賓奴一役，中堅拿祖費南迪斯將會串演左閘，而小將阿舒拉夫則會擔任右閘。除了缺陣皇馬的比賽之外，丹尼爾卡華積也將缺陣西班牙即將舉行的兩場國際賽。<br />\n<br />\n25歲的丹尼爾卡華積出生自皇馬青訓，於2012年加盟利華古遜，因為表現出色而在1季後被回購，立即成為正選右閘。"},{"pid":"99c93fb13a3ea75b9a8ef6144d834a40312316b4","tid":420215,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T08:35:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8220faaca94d9df1c4aab0b90971efa11309f739","tid":420215,"uid":993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T08:37:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b84b8c11f8317cb5a31d8c9f240c0fd9ff17748b","tid":420215,"uid":54373,"like":0,"di